PWA + Supabase persistence + API for Custom GPT

PWA:
- manifest.json with app metadata and theme colors
- SVG icon (frog + sword) + generated PNG icons (192, 512, apple-touch)
- Service worker with cache-first for static, network-first for pages
- Meta tags: apple-web-app-capable, theme-color, viewport lock
- Service worker registration in root layout

Supabase:
- Schema: kv_store, activity_log, chat_messages tables
- usePersistedState hook: localStorage instant hydration + Supabase sync
- Debounced writes (300ms) to avoid hammering the DB
- Graceful fallback: works without Supabase (localStorage only)
- Migrated all pages from useLocalStorage to usePersistedState

API endpoints for Custom GPT Actions:
- GET/POST /api/quests — read/add quests
- GET/POST /api/log — read/add activity log entries
- GET /api/status — system overview (quests, XP, log count)
- OpenAPI spec at /openapi.json for ChatGPT Actions
- Bearer token auth via API_SECRET env var
